Package edu.xtec.jclic.edit

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Editable
    Classes that implement this interface have always an associated Editor.
    Editor.EditorListener  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EditDialog
    This class is a basic template of a JDialog useful for editing objects.
    Editor
    This generic class allows to modify the content and properties of an associated Editable object.
    EditorAction
    This abstract class provides a base to create Action objects related to Editors.
    EditorPanel
    This class is a CtrlPanel specialized to deal with Editor objects.
    EditorTreePanel
